---
title: Sri Lankan Chickpea Curry with Garlic Rice & Toasted Coconut
description: If we had to list our favourite things about Sri Lankan food, we’d be here all night. But one of the best things is the variety of vegetarian options available – there are so many ways to make veggies and legumes exciting! This chickpea curry uses a mild yet flavourful paste, plus tomatoes and a dash of cream to create a warm, comforting dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ftc-sri-lankan-chickpea-curry-e2b8ad00.jpg
